  "prompt": "What are the best coffee shops with Wi-Fi in San Francisco for evening work?",
  "response": "San Francisco has many great coffee shops that provide Wi-Fi and a conducive environment for evening work. Here are some top recommendations:\n\n1. **Ritual Coffee Roasters** - Located in the Mission District, Ritual Coffee Roasters offers a vibrant atmosphere and reliable Wi-Fi, making it a popular spot for working. The coffee is excellent, and the space is conducive for concentration.\n\n2. **The Mill** - Situated on Divisadero Street, The Mill is known for its artisan bread and coffee. It has a spacious seating area with a relaxed ambiance, ideal for evening work sessions. Wi-Fi is available, and the environment is generally quiet.\n\n3. **Four Barrel Coffee** - Another Mission District favorite, Four Barrel Coffee provides a rustic yet modern setting with plenty of seating. The Wi-Fi is strong, and the shop stays open until the evening, providing a good atmosphere for work.\n\n4. **Sightglass Coffee** - With multiple locations, including one in SoMa, Sightglass Coffee offers a stylish and spacious environment with great Wi-Fi. The SoMa location stays open late and is perfect for evening work.\n\n5. **Cafe R\u00e9veille** - Located in Mission Bay, Cafe R\u00e9veille has a cozy atmosphere and good Wi-Fi. It\u2019s a great spot for working late into the evening, with a menu that includes both coffee and light meals.\n\n6. **Coffee Bar** - With locations in Mission and Potrero Hill, Coffee Bar provides a welcoming space with ample seating and dependable Wi-Fi. The Mission location, in particular, stays open later and is a good choice for evening work.\n\n7. **Workshop Cafe** - Located in FiDi, Workshop Cafe is designed specifically for working professionals. It has strong Wi-Fi, plenty of power outlets, and stays open until late, making it an ideal spot for evening work.\n\n8. **Philz Coffee** - With numerous locations around the city, Philz Coffee offers a laid-back environment with good Wi-Fi. Many locations stay open late, providing a comfortable space for evening work.\n\nThese coffee shops are well-regarded for their ambiance, Wi-Fi quality, and suitability for working in the evenings. Consider visiting them to find the one that best suits your needs.",
